ins. Multi-ingredient formulation; consult the package leaflet for the complete ingredient list and adult dosing instructions.","key_benefits":[{"icon":"\ud83d\udc9b","text":"Supports female fertility"},{"icon":"\ud83c\udf3f","text":"Folic + inositol blend"},{"icon":"\ud83d\udcaa","text":"Aids reproductive wellness"},{"icon":"\ud83d\udee1\ufe0f","text":"Doctor-recommended"}],"faq":[{"q":"How long should I take it before conceiving?","a":"Most fertility specialists recommend 1\u20133 months of prep before trying to conceive."},{"q":"Can I take it during pregnancy?","a":"Many formulas transition into prenatal support \u2014 confirm with your doctor."},{"q":"Any side effects?","a":"Generally well tolerated. Stop and consult your doctor if unusual symptoms appear."}],"usage_tips":"Take consistently \u2014 fertility nutrition needs steady daily intake. Pair with a balanced diet, reduced caffeine and good sleep. Store in a cool dry place.","social_proof":""},{"id":"6e20f906-e654-4812-ae86-32ae95ded60a","how_to_use":"Take one tablet or sachet daily with water, or as directed by your fertility specialist.","ingredients":"L-Carnitine, Zinc, Selenium, Coenzyme Q10, Vitamin E, Folic Acid. Multi-ingredient formulation; consult the package leaflet for the complete ingredient list and adult dosing instructions.","key_benefits":[{"icon":"\ud83d\udcaa","text":"Supports male fertility"},{"icon":"\ud83c\udf3f","text":"Antioxidant + zinc blend"},{"icon":"\u26a1","text":"Aids reproductive wellness"},{"icon":"\ud83d\udee1\ufe0f","text":"Doctor-recommended"}],"faq":[{"q":"How long should I take it before trying to conceive?","a":"Most fertility specialists recommend 3 months of prep \u2014 sperm production takes about 72 days."},{"q":"Can my wife take this too?","a":"Repro-M is formulated for men. Repro-F is the partner formula for women."},{"q":"Any side effects?","a":"Generally well tolerated. Stop and consult your doctor if unusual symptoms appear."}],"usage_tips":"Take consistently \