ly prescribed in pregnancy \u2014 confirm dosage with your doctor."},{"q":"Will it cause constipation?","a":"Some iron supplements can. Increase water and fibre intake to ease this."},{"q":"Can I take it with tea?","a":"Avoid \u2014 tea and coffee can reduce iron absorption. Take with vitamin C-rich food instead."}],"usage_tips":"Take with orange juice or another Vitamin C source to boost absorption. Don''t take at the same time as calcium or thyroid medication. Store in a cool dry place.","social_proof":""},{"id":"91f49013-8c40-4b48-967e-deae5bcad689","how_to_use":"Give the recommended number of drops as per age/weight, using the included dropper, or as directed by your paediatrician.","ingredients":"Multi-ingredient formulation; consult the package leaflet for the complete ingredient list and dosing instructions.","key_benefits":[{"icon":"\ud83d\udc9b","text":"Easy-dose paediatric drops"},{"icon":"\ud83c\udf3f","text":"Gentle daily wellness"},{"icon":"\ud83d\udca7","text":"Supports growth and immunity"},{"icon":"\ud83d\udee1\ufe0f","text":"Doctor-formulated"}],"faq":[{"q":"What age is it for?","a":"Confirm appropriate age with your paediatrician \u2014 typically formulated for infants and young children."},{"q":"Does it have any taste?","a":"Most paediatric drops have a mild pleasant taste \u2014 check the leaflet."},{"q":"How should I store it?","a":"Keep in a cool dry place. Some drops require refrigeration after opening \u2014 check the leaflet."}],"usage_tips":"Use the included dropper for precise dosing. Keep the bottle tightly closed and out of reach of children. Discard after the expiry on the bottle.","social_proof":""},{"id":"1952391d-d7a5-4585-8708-4f5335449174","how_to_use":"Take one tablet daily with water, preferably with food, or as directed by your gynaecologist.","ingredients":"Folic Acid, Vitamin B12, Iron. Multi-ingredient formulation; consult the package leaflet for the complete ingredient list and adult dosing instructions.","key_benefits":[{"icon":"\ud83d\udc9b","text":"Folic acid for women"},{"icon":"\ud83c\udf3f","text":"Supports prenatal wellness"},{"icon":"\ud83d\udcaa","text":"Aids healthy pregnancy"},{"icon":"\ud83d\udee1\ufe0f","text":"Doctor-recommended"}],"faq":[{"q":"Is it safe in early pregnancy?","a":"Folic acid is commonly prescribed in early pregnancy \u2014 confirm dosage with your doctor."},{"q":"When should I start taking it?","a":"Ideally 1\u20133 months before conception and through the first trimester at minimum."},{"q":"Any side effects?","a":"Generally well tolerated. Stop and consult your doctor if unusual symptoms appear."}],"usage_tips":"Take at the same time daily for consistency. Pair with a balanced diet rich in leafy greens. Store in a cool dry place.","social_proof":""},{"id":"72666671-675c-440d-8ce0-6eefb87035a8","how_to_use":"Take as directed on the packaging or by your physician.","ingredients":"Multi-ingredient formulation; consult the package leaflet for the complete ingredient list and adult dosing instructions.","key_benefits":[{"icon":"\ud83c\udf3f","text":"Daily wellness support"},{"icon":"\ud83d\udcaa","text":"Supports body resilience"},{"icon":"\ud83d\udee1\ufe0f","text":"Doctor-recommended formula"},{"icon":"\u26a1","text":"Easy to take"}],"faq":[{"q":"When should I take it?","a":"Follow the directions on the packaging or your doctor''s advice."},{"q":"Any side effects?","a":"Generally well tolerated. Stop and consult your doctor if unusual symptoms appear."},{"q":"Is it safe in pregnancy?","a":"Consult your doctor before use in pregnancy or breastfeeding."}],"usage_tips":"Maintain a consistent daily routine. Stay hydrated. Store in a cool dry place away from direct sunlight.","social_proof":""},{"id":"cbe288dd-ebba-42d8-9e44-f307f00783af","how_to_use":"Take one tablet daily with water, or as directed by your physician.","ingredients":"Serratiopeptidase 100 mg. Multi-ingredient formulation; consult the package leaflet for the complete ingredient list and adult dosing instructions.","key_benefits":[{"icon":"\ud83d\udee1\ufe0f","text":"Supports inflammation response"},{"icon":"\ud83c\udf3f","text":"Enzyme-based daily aid"},{"icon":"\ud83d\udcaa","text":"Helps post-injury recovery"},{"icon":"\u26a1","text":"Easy daily tablet"}],"faq":[{"q":"When should I take it?","a":"Most users take it on an empty stomach \u2014 30 minutes before meals or 2 hours after."},{"q":"Any side effects?","a":"Generally well tolerated. Stop and consult your doctor if you experience GI discomfort."},{"q":"Is it safe in pregnancy?","a":"Avoid during pregnancy and breastfeeding unless prescribed by your doctor."}],"usage_tips":"Take with water on an empty stomach for best enzyme activity. Avoid food for at least 30 minutes after dosing. Store in a cool dry place.","social_proof":""},{"id":"1f50da89-eab8-4cad-b41e-e9ae95c63427","how_to_use":"Take or apply as directed on the packaging or by your physician.","ingredients":"Multi-ingredient formulation; consult the package leaflet for the complete ingredient list and dosing instructions.","key_benefits":[{"icon":"\ud83c\udf3f","text":"Supports throat and voice"},{"icon":"\ud83d\udee1\ufe0f","text":"Soothing daily formula"},{"icon":"\ud83d\udca7","text":"Gentle on the system"},{"icon":"\ud83d\udcaa","text":"Doctor-recommended"}],"faq":[{"q":"When should I take it?","a":"Follow the directions on the packaging or your doctor''s advice."},{"q":"Any side effects?","a":"Generally well tolerated. Stop and consult your doctor if unusual symptoms appear."},{"q":"Is it safe long-term?","a":"Usually yes when used as directed. Confirm with your doctor."}],"usage_tips":"Stay well hydrated to support throat comfort. Avoid cold drinks during voice strain. Store in a cool dry place.","social_proof":""},{"id":"cc411c3f-b6dc-4af6-9e90-9f3d6be233ae","how_to_use":"Take each supplement in the combo as directed on the individual packaging, typically one dose daily with food.","ingredients":"Bundle contains calcium, vitamin D, magnesium and joint-support supplements. Multi-ingredient formulation; consult the package leaflet for the complete ingredient list and dosing instructions.","key_benefits":[{"icon":"\ud83d\udcaa","text":"Strengthens bones and joints"},{"icon":"\ud83c\udf3f","text":"Calcium + Vit D + glucosamine"},{"icon":"\ud83d\udee1\ufe0f","text":"Supports skeletal wellness"},{"icon":"\u2728","text":"Bundled at a saving"}],"faq":[{"q":"Who is this combo for?","a":"Adults concerned about bone density, joint comfort or those at higher risk of osteoporosis."},{"q":"How long should I take it?","a":"Most users do a 2\u20133 month course. Confirm with your doctor."},{"q":"Can I take all items together?","a":"Some need to be spaced (e.g. calcium and iron). Check the individual packaging or consult your doctor."}],"usage_tips":"Take calcium with dinner for better absorption. Pair with weight-bearing exercise. Keep all bottles in one place and set a daily reminder.","social_proof":""},{"id":"be320e34-760a-4e29-a3d9-239174440334","how_to_use":"Take or apply as directed on the packaging or by your physician.","ingredients":"Multi-ingredient formulation; consult the package leaflet for the complete ingredient list and dosing instructions.","key_benefits":[{"icon":"\ud83d\udc9b","text":"Supports women''s wellness"},{"icon":"\ud83c\udf3f","text":"Daily nutritional blend"},{"icon":"\ud83d\udcaa","text":"Helps everyday balance"},{"icon":"\ud83d\udee1\ufe0f","text":"Doctor-recommended"}],"faq":[{"q":"Is it safe in pregnancy?","a":"Consult your gynaecologist before use in pregnancy or breastfeeding."},{"q":"Any side effects?","a":"Generally well tolerated. Stop and consult your doctor if unusual symptoms appear."},{"q":"How long should I take it?","a":"Most courses run 1\u20133 months. Confirm with your doctor."}],"usage_tips":"Take with food to prevent stomach upset. Stay hydrated. Store in a cool dry place away from sunlight.","social_proof":""},{"id":"1a1b4235-1bc0-4b35-9322-d91e81a126fe","how_to_use":"Apply a generous even layer to clean, dry skin as the last step of your morning routine. Use fingers or a sponge to blend. Reapply every 2 hours in the sun.","ingredients":"Active: Octinoxate, Zinc Oxide. Other: Aqua/Water, Glycerin, Hyaluronic Acid, Niacinamide, Iron Oxides for sheer tint, Tocopheryl Acetate, Dimethicone, Phenoxyethanol.","key_benefits":[{"icon":"\u2600\ufe0f","text":"SPF 46 broad-spectrum"},{"icon":"\ud83c\udf38","text":"Sheer universal tint"},{"icon":"\ud83d\udca7","text":"Hydrating moisturiser in one"},{"icon":"\ud83d\udee1\ufe0f","text":"Lightweight 3-in-1 formula"}],"faq":[{"q":"Will it leave a white cast on darker skin?","a":"No \u2014 the universal tint adapts to fair to deep skin without a white or grey cast."},{"q":"Can I wear makeup over it?","a":"Yes, it works beautifully as a base under foundation or alone for a no-makeup look."},{"q":"Is it suitable for oily skin?","a":"Yes, the lightweight formula sets to a soft semi-matte finish."}],"usage_tips":"Apply two finger-lengths for full face SPF protection. Reapply throughout the day, especially before outdoor exposure. Shake gently before each use.","social_proof":""},{"id":"e4ad1a1c-7a4f-4e7a-b6f7-a5c21a7ea10a","how_to_use":"Take or apply as directed on the packaging or by your physician.","ingredients":"Multi-ingredient formulation; consult the package leaflet for the complete ingredient list and dosing instructions.","key_benefits":[{"icon":"\ud83c\udf3f","text":"Daily wellness blend"},{"icon":"\ud83d\udcaa","text":"Supports body resilience"},{"icon":"\ud83d\udee1\ufe0f","text":"Doctor-recommended formula"},{"icon":"\u26a1","text":"Easy to use"}],"faq":[{"q":"When should I take it?","a":"Follow the directions on the packaging or your doctor''s advice."},{"q":"Any side effects?","a":"Generally well tolerated. Stop and consult your doctor if unusual symptoms appear."},{"q":"Is it safe in pregnancy?","a":"Consult your doctor before use in pregnancy or breastfeeding."}],"usage_tips":"Maintain a consistent daily routine. Stay hydrated. Store in a cool dry place away from direct sunlight.","social_proof":""},{"id":"643397e8-5b9a-4706-af12-e652b4085125","how_to_use":"Take one tablet daily with water, or as directed by your physician.","ingredients":"Calcium, Vitamin D3, Magnesium. Multi-ingredient formulation; consult the package leaflet for the complete ingredient list and adult dosing instructions.","key_benefits":[{"icon":"\ud83d\udcaa","text":"Strengthens bones"},{"icon":"\ud83c\udf3f","text":"Calcium + Vit D blend"},{"icon":"\ud83d\udee1\ufe0f","text":"Supports bone density"},{"icon":"\u2728","text":"Easy daily tablet"}],"faq":[{"q":"Is it safe in pregnancy?","a":"Calcium and Vitamin D are commonly prescribed in pregnancy \u2014 confirm dosage with your doctor."},{"q":"When should I take it?","a":"Take after dinner \u2014 calcium absorbs better in the evening with food."},{"q":"Any side effects?","a":"Mild constipation may occur. Increase water and fibre to ease this."}],"usage_tips":"Space from iron and thyroid medications by at least 2 hours. Stay hydrated. Pair with weight-bearing exercise for stronger bones.","social_proof":""},{"id":"47c05c71-6af5-4592-a675-44630bfb67f3","how_to_use":"Take one tablet or sachet daily with water, or as directed by your physician.","ingredients":"Vitamin K2, Vitamin D3. Multi-ingredient formulation; consult the package leaflet for the complete ingredient list and adult dosing instructions.","key_benefits":[{"icon":"\ud83d\udcaa","text":"Vit K2 + D3 for bones"},{"icon":"\ud83c\udf3f","text":"Supports calcium absorption"},{"icon":"\ud83d\udee1\ufe0f","text":"Helps bone density"},{"icon":"\u2728","text":"Daily skeletal support"}],"faq":[{"q":"Why combine Vitamin K with D3?","a":"Vitamin K2 helps direct calcium into bones rather than soft tissue, working synergistically with Vit D3."},{"q":"Is it safe in pregnancy?","a":"Confirm dosage with your doctor before use during pregnancy."},{"q":"Can I take it with calcium?","a":"Yes \u2014 Vit K2 and D3 enhance calcium effectiveness."}],"usage_tips":"Take with a meal containing healthy fats (yoghurt, nuts, eggs) for better absorption. Stay hydrated. Store in a cool dry place.","social_proof":""},{"id":"1d3a614f-2855-4d9a-92e0-009ebf4f652b","how_to_use":"Take each supplement in the combo as directed on the individual packaging, typically one dose daily with food.","ingredients":"Bundle contains multi-vitamin and women''s health supplements. Multi-ingredient formulation; consult the package leaflet for the complete ingredient list and dosing instructions.","key_benefits":[{"icon":"\ud83d\udc9b","text":"Complete female wellness combo"},{"icon":"\ud83c\udf3f","text":"Hormonal balance blend"},{"icon":"\ud83d\udcaa","text":"Supports daily vitality"},{"icon":"\ud83d\udee1\ufe0f","text":"Bundled at a saving"}],"faq":[{"q":"Who is this combo for?","a":"Adult women looking for hormonal balance, daily nutrition and overall wellness."},{"q":"Is it safe in pregnancy?","a":"Some items may not be suitable in pregnancy \u2014 consult your gynaecologist before starting."},{"q":"How long should I take it?","a":"Most users do a 1\u20133 month course. Confirm with your doctor."}],"usage_tips":"Keep all bottles in one place and set a daily reminder. Pair with a balanced diet, exercise and good sleep. Store in a cool dry place.","social_proof":""},{"id":"2a518517-f425-41b4-8850-542611f7f649","how_to_use":"Take as directed on the packaging or by your physician.","ingredients":"Multi-ingredient formulation; consult the package leaflet for the complete ingredient list and adult dosing instructions.","key_benefits":[{"icon":"\ud83d\udcaa","text":"Supports daily fitness"},{"icon":"\ud83c\udf3f","text":"Energy and recovery blend"},{"icon":"\u26a1","text":"Helps performance"},{"icon":"\ud83d\udee1\ufe0f","text":"Doctor-recommended formula"}],"faq":[{"q":"When should I take it?","a":"Most users take it before or after workouts \u2014 follow your doctor''s advice."},{"q":"Any side effects?","a":"Generally well tolerated. Stop and consult your doctor if unusual symptoms appear."},{"q":"Is it safe with caffeine?","a":"Usually yes, but you may need less caffeine than usual. Listen to your body."}],"usage_tips":"Pair with consistent sleep and balanced nutrition. Stay well hydrated, especially around workouts. Store in a cool dry place.","social_proof":""}]'::jsonb) AS j
)
UPDATE public.products p
   SET how_to_use    = COALESCE(NULLIF(p.how_to_use, ''),    s.how_to_use),
       ingredients   = COALESCE(NULLIF(p.ingredients, ''),   s.ingredients),
       key_benefits  = CASE
                         WHEN p.key_benefits IS NULL OR jsonb_array_length(p.key_benefits) = 0
                         THEN s.key_benefits
                         ELSE p.key_benefits
                       END,
       faq           = CASE
                         WHEN p.faq IS NULL OR jsonb_array_length(p.faq) = 0
                         THEN s.faq
                         ELSE p.faq
                       END,
       usage_tips    = COALESCE(NULLIF(p.usage_tips, ''),    s.usage_tips),
       social_proof  = COALESCE(NULLIF(p.social_proof, ''),  s.social_proof)
  FROM src s
 WHERE p.id = s.id;
